Text:
Wrong category!

Resolution...........: 720 x 384 Pixels

Is NOT High Res!

Video < 1280 x 720p are not Video>Highres

Read it here:
https://forum.suprbay.org/forumdisplay.php?fid=29

Moved to Video -> Movies

720p -> 1280x720p

Video under 1280 x 720 pixels won't consider as High-Res Movies.
Avoid wrong description in the next time and choose appropriate category.
